00:02:05.590 --> 00:02:06.640
What are you doing here?

00:02:06.640 --> 00:02:08.220
Why are you running like this?

00:02:08.220 --> 00:02:15.540
♪The endless shackle of darkness♪

00:02:19.300 --> 00:02:23.940
♪Come to me, my love♪

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:27.560
I'm pleased you're fine.

00:02:27.580 --> 00:02:28.540
♪No more worries♪

00:02:29.060 --> 00:02:32.940
♪There will always be a gap♪

00:02:33.180 --> 00:02:35.620
♪Crush it♪

00:02:36.120 --> 00:02:36.910
Chu Minghui...

00:02:37.750 --> 00:02:38.560
Chu Minghui!

00:02:38.580 --> 00:02:40.340
♪Keep it to yourself♪

00:02:48.500 --> 00:02:51.020
[Cunji Hospital of Jiang City]

00:02:58.360 --> 00:02:59.150
Chu Minghui.

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:04.960
It's been so long

00:03:07.800 --> 00:03:10.030
since we've had
such a peaceful moment together.

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:12.150
Chu Minghui,

00:03:13.280 --> 00:03:14.750
ever since I met you again,

00:03:15.520 --> 00:03:16.960
it's either been quarrels

00:03:18.630 --> 00:03:20.360
or cold, detached transactions.

00:03:21.800 --> 00:03:23.870
If sharing a tender moment with you

00:03:23.960 --> 00:03:25.030
puts you at risk,

00:03:26.840 --> 00:03:28.680
I'd rather you never speak to me again

00:03:29.560 --> 00:03:31.030
when you wake up.

00:03:57.150 --> 00:03:58.080
Thank you.

00:03:58.630 --> 00:04:00.430
Is that all you wanted to say to me?

00:04:01.240 --> 00:04:02.120
Chu Minghui,

00:04:02.360 --> 00:04:04.150
you risked your life to save me.

00:04:05.150 --> 00:04:06.710
You clearly care about me.

00:04:06.960 --> 00:04:08.430
Why won't you admit it?

00:04:10.870 --> 00:04:11.680
Chu Minghui,

00:04:12.870 --> 00:04:14.960
can we stop deceiving
and tormenting each other?

00:04:15.400 --> 00:04:16.750
Aren't you afraid

00:04:17.190 --> 00:04:18.310
that one day you won't get to me in time

00:04:18.830 --> 00:04:20.160
and I'll die before I hear a word

00:04:20.160 --> 00:04:21.070
from you?

00:04:21.510 --> 00:04:22.190
I...

00:04:45.190 --> 00:04:46.920
You've really underestimated

00:04:47.510 --> 00:04:48.830
how much I love you.

00:05:55.680 --> 00:05:57.120
They can't sell opium

00:05:57.190 --> 00:05:58.750
or kill Gu Tongpei.

00:05:59.040 --> 00:06:00.830
The deal with Chu Yan
is at a standstill too.

00:06:02.240 --> 00:06:04.630
Where did I even find
such a bunch of useless fools?

00:06:07.270 --> 00:06:08.270
This has dragged on too long,

00:06:08.830 --> 00:06:10.160
and the losses are too heavy.

00:06:10.160 --> 00:06:11.120
If we want money,

00:06:11.800 --> 00:06:13.040
there's only one way left.

00:06:14.070 --> 00:06:15.270
We'll follow your order.

00:06:16.190 --> 00:06:17.190
This quarter's military supplies

00:06:17.440 --> 00:06:19.360
will soon arrive.

00:06:19.920 --> 00:06:20.870
Do it the usual way.

00:06:22.270 --> 00:06:23.070
Understood.

00:06:23.680 --> 00:06:25.240
When the funds come through,

00:06:25.240 --> 00:06:27.950
I'll keep the actual spending

00:06:28.270 --> 00:06:29.720
within twenty percent.

00:06:30.070 --> 00:06:30.870
No,

00:06:32.040 --> 00:06:33.160
within ten percent.

00:06:34.830 --> 00:06:35.630
Ten percent.

00:07:12.360 --> 00:07:14.160
Have you realized you lost big

00:07:14.360 --> 00:07:15.560
talking back to me before?

00:07:17.510 --> 00:07:18.630
I just think

00:07:19.000 --> 00:07:22.240
lies and concealment are not love.

00:07:31.950 --> 00:07:32.830
Yes,

00:07:33.430 --> 00:07:34.480
only love is love.

00:07:44.870 --> 00:07:45.870
There's a problem.

00:07:47.000 --> 00:07:48.510
How are you going
to explain to Gu Tongce

00:07:48.830 --> 00:07:50.870
that you didn't go home last night?

00:07:52.480 --> 00:07:53.270
Right.

00:07:53.600 --> 00:07:54.800
And yesterday

00:07:54.800 --> 00:07:56.630
was supposed to be
our wedding anniversary.

00:08:05.680 --> 00:08:07.310
It's not a real anniversary.

00:08:07.750 --> 00:08:08.630
He and I

00:08:09.310 --> 00:08:11.120
were never truly married.

00:08:11.630 --> 00:08:13.270
It's just something for appearances.

00:08:17.310 --> 00:08:19.360
Then why play along with him?

00:08:19.950 --> 00:08:23.270
What binds me is never the marriage.

00:08:24.240 --> 00:08:25.070
It's Hongdou.

00:08:25.750 --> 00:08:28.070
Every year on this day,

00:08:28.160 --> 00:08:29.360
he made me go through

00:08:29.360 --> 00:08:31.040
that hollow ritual with him.

00:08:33.960 --> 00:08:36.080
But he didn't seem to care yesterday.

00:08:39.240 --> 00:08:40.270
I have a plan,

00:08:40.600 --> 00:08:41.870
but I'll need your cooperation.

00:09:01.150 --> 00:09:02.910
Outrageous.

00:09:03.320 --> 00:09:04.910
You stayed out all night
with another man?

00:09:05.870 --> 00:09:06.630
Tongce,

00:09:06.960 --> 00:09:08.270
did you forget?

00:09:08.630 --> 00:09:10.030
Yesterday was your fourth anniversary

00:09:10.030 --> 00:09:11.240
with Minghui.

00:09:11.510 --> 00:09:12.550
She was so upset

00:09:12.550 --> 00:09:13.870
that she walked out.

00:09:14.360 --> 00:09:16.080
I happened to run into her
during patrol this morning,

00:09:16.080 --> 00:09:17.630
so I brought her back.

00:09:18.720 --> 00:09:19.840
Don't tell him.

00:09:20.030 --> 00:09:21.440
You always stayed home with me

00:09:21.510 --> 00:09:23.150
at this time of year.

00:09:23.480 --> 00:09:26.080
I always thought that was
our unspoken understanding.

00:09:26.670 --> 00:09:27.910
Now I see,

00:09:28.360 --> 00:09:29.510
it was only in my head.

00:09:33.510 --> 00:09:34.320
Tongce,

00:09:35.200 --> 00:09:36.440
now that you've gotten together,

00:09:36.510 --> 00:09:38.270
you should cherish her.

00:09:39.200 --> 00:09:40.440
These details

00:09:40.630 --> 00:09:42.240
may seem trivial to you,

00:09:42.750 --> 00:09:44.270
but to a woman,

00:09:44.600 --> 00:09:46.120
they're vital.

00:09:54.870 --> 00:09:55.630
What's this?

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:58.750
I heard from Minghui
that you haven't taken

00:09:58.750 --> 00:09:59.720
any wedding photos yet.

00:10:00.080 --> 00:10:00.510
So,

00:10:00.910 --> 00:10:02.510
I arranged a photographer

00:10:02.630 --> 00:10:03.670
and rented outfits

00:10:03.870 --> 00:10:05.080
so you can make up for it.

00:10:05.360 --> 00:10:08.000
Think of it as making up
for yesterday's anniversary.

00:10:16.720 --> 00:10:17.750
You two

00:10:18.270 --> 00:10:20.630
had better not try any tricks.

00:10:20.910 --> 00:10:21.750
What do you mean?

00:10:22.030 --> 00:10:23.360
If you don't want to take them, fine.

00:10:23.510 --> 00:10:24.480
Forget it.

00:10:24.480 --> 00:10:25.270
Wait.

00:10:26.240 --> 00:10:27.150
Let's do it.

00:10:28.240 --> 00:10:29.440
How can we not take photos?

00:10:30.480 --> 00:10:32.870
Don't waste Tongpei's effort.

00:11:10.630 --> 00:11:11.480
Beautiful.

00:11:16.080 --> 00:11:16.870
Tongce,

00:11:17.510 --> 00:11:18.840
the champagne's ready.

00:11:20.150 --> 00:11:20.960
Let's go.

00:11:22.240 --> 00:11:23.030
Tongce,

00:11:23.720 --> 00:11:25.080
why don't you change into your uniform?

00:11:25.390 --> 00:11:27.150
That would make it more meaningful.

00:11:35.870 --> 00:11:36.670
Wait for me.

00:11:43.120 --> 00:11:44.630
Very thoughtful.

00:11:53.030 --> 00:11:54.670
You can also go upstairs

00:11:54.670 --> 00:11:56.360
and see if Tongce needs anything.

00:11:56.360 --> 00:11:57.120
Yes.

00:12:10.550 --> 00:12:11.440
Do I look good?

00:12:54.320 --> 00:12:55.200
When

00:12:56.000 --> 00:12:57.750
will I finally be able
to kiss you openly?

00:12:58.870 --> 00:13:00.550
Once everything settles down.

00:13:02.840 --> 00:13:03.910
It won't be long.

00:13:08.360 --> 00:13:09.320
Do I look good?

00:13:10.390 --> 00:13:11.200
You do.

00:13:31.240 --> 00:13:33.270
You can be a bit closer.

00:13:47.820 --> 00:13:49.460
The bride looks a little nervous.

00:13:49.980 --> 00:13:50.940
That's fine. Let's try this.

00:13:50.940 --> 00:13:51.700
The groom sits,

00:13:51.700 --> 00:13:53.700
and the bride stands behind,
resting her hands on his shoulders.

00:14:07.940 --> 00:14:08.740
Good.

00:14:09.660 --> 00:14:10.460
Smile.

00:14:11.420 --> 00:14:13.020
One, two, three.

00:14:17.340 --> 00:14:18.180
Great, very good.

00:14:22.220 --> 00:14:23.020
Ce,

00:14:24.020 --> 00:14:26.420
why don't we call Tongpei over

00:14:26.420 --> 00:14:27.860
and take a family photo?

00:14:29.780 --> 00:14:30.580
Ce.

00:14:32.020 --> 00:14:32.820
Okay.

00:14:33.500 --> 00:14:34.380
Come on, Tongpei.

00:14:47.780 --> 00:14:49.100
All right, everyone in place.

00:14:50.100 --> 00:14:51.480
Three, two, one.

00:15:08.820 --> 00:15:09.470
I told you

00:15:10.680 --> 00:15:12.360
I won't keep you waiting long.

00:15:22.260 --> 00:15:23.030
What's wrong?

00:15:26.340 --> 00:15:27.100
Nothing.

00:15:27.100 --> 00:15:28.180
Just out of focus.

00:15:28.180 --> 00:15:29.300
Let's take another one.

00:15:32.740 --> 00:15:34.100
Three, two, one.

00:15:36.140 --> 00:15:37.260
Great. Excellent.

00:15:38.180 --> 00:15:39.220
Once the photos are developed,

00:15:39.870 --> 00:15:41.060
frame them and send them over.

00:15:47.980 --> 00:15:49.420
Once this busy period is over,

00:15:49.820 --> 00:15:50.900
I'll spend proper time with you.

00:15:51.580 --> 00:15:54.000
Okay, I'll go upstairs and get changed.

00:16:30.340 --> 00:16:30.780
Sir,

00:16:30.940 --> 00:16:31.740
understood.

00:16:32.140 --> 00:16:33.420
When the photos are ready,

00:16:33.900 --> 00:16:35.140
I'll bring them straight to you.

